headline: Gibraltar Q2 Earnings & Sales Lag Estimates, Both Rise Y/Y, Stock Down
summary: ROCK's Q2 EPS rises 11% but misses estimates, while strong M&A and infrastructure gains drive 13% revenue growth.

headline: Martin Marietta's Q2 Earnings Top, Revenues Miss, '25 View Revised
summary: MLM's Q2 EPS rose 14% and beat estimates, while revenues missed slightly; 2025 guidance has been revised with higher EBITDA targets.
